snippet.title: Extra Butter: Celebrity Interviews & Movie Reviews
snippet.description:
We talk about movies the way you talk about movies!
Extra Butter is for real people, looking for real talk and real access to the latest movies. 
Hear from the biggest stars from the biggest movies, with interviews from Mark S. Allen.
Get reviews from people who love movies.
Be sure to subscribe and let us know what you think!
